    - **Unified `code→symbol` variable naming across codebase**
        - `stock_zh_a_hist_child.py`: `code→bs_code`, `raw_code→symbol`; sink calls `upsert_bars()` (v2) instead of `upsert_stock_zh_a_hist()` (legacy)
        - `stock_zh_a_hist_parent.py`: `code_list→symbol_list`, `codes→symbols`, `code_infos→symbol_infos`; calls `get_securities()` / `get_bars_last_update()` (v2)
        - `campaign.py`: `code_infos→symbol_infos`; migrated to v2 API
        - `phoenixA_client.py`: removed `"code"` backward-compat field from `get_securities()` return
